English: <color=red>://ERROR: Door is connected to an unstable power source. High risk of operation failure. </color>
Description: A text string that appears on screen when the player attempts to open a door which is locked due to an emergency lockdown. Don't alter the RichText tags.

French.Translation: <color=red>://ERREUR : la porte est connectée à une source d'alimentation instable. Risque de dysfonctionnement élevé. </color>

Italian.Translation: <color=red>://ERRORE: la porta è collegata a una fonte di alimentazione instabile. Elevato rischio di guasto operativo. </color>

German.Translation: <color=red>://FEHLER: Die Tür ist an eine instabile Stromquelle angeschlossen. Hohes Risiko eines Betriebsausfalls.</color>

Spanish.Translation: <color=red>://ERROR: Puerta conectada a una fuente de energía inestable. Alto riesgo de error de funcionamiento. </color>

Russian.Translation: <color=red>://ОШИБКА. Дверь подключена к нестабильному источнику питания. Высока вероятность сбоя</color>.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: <color=red>://ERRO: Porta conectada com uma fonte de energia instável. Alto risco de falha na operação. </color>

Polish.Translation: <color=red>://BŁĄD: Drzwi są podłączone do niestabilnego źródła zasilania. Znaczne ryzyko wystąpienia awarii. </color>

Japanese.Translation: <color=red>://エラー：ドアの電力源が不安定。動作不良の危険高し。</color>

Korean.Translation: <color=red>://오류: 문이 불안정한 전력 공급원에 연결되어 있습니다. 작동이 중지될 위험이 큽니다. </color>

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: <color=red>://錯誤：門連接到不穩定的電源。有高風險會操作失敗。</color>

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: <color=red>://错误：门所连接的电源不稳定。运行失败风险较高。</color>
